---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '21 June 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Ketentuan penggunaan bot dan layanan Vanillate Studio."
>
  <section class="container-page pt-20 md:pt-28 pb-12 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-6">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tightest text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
      Terms of Service
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 dark:text-cream-300/60 font-mono">
      Last Updated: {lastUpdated}
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container-page pb-24 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="space-y-12 text-ink-700 dark:text-cream-200 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By inviting, accessing, or using Vanillate ("the Bot"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with these terms, you must stop using the Bot immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Vanillate is a Discord bot that provides interactive word-chain (Sambung Kata) gameplay and related features. These include, but are not limited to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Multiplayer gameplay systems</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Player statistics and progression tracking</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Leaderboards and ranking systems</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Economy, boost, or reward systems</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Achievements and community engagement features</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We may modify, update, add, or remove features at any time without prior notice to improve service quality or ensure stability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Users agree to use Vanillate responsibly and must:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Follow Discord Terms of Service and Community Guidelines</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Use the Bot only for its intended purposes</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Not exploit bugs, glitches, or unintended mechanics</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Not use automated scripts, bots, or external tools to gain unfair advantages</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Not interfere with or disrupt the Bot's normal operation</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">Violation of these rules may result in restricted access to the Bot.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">4. Server Owner Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Server owners and administrators are responsible for:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Managing the permissions granted to Vanillate</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Ensuring the Bot is used appropriately within their server</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Removing the Bot if they no longer wish to use it</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">5. Data Usage and Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Vanillate may process and store limited Discord-related data necessary for functionality, including user IDs, server IDs, and gameplay-related data such as statistics, progression, and configuration settings.
        </p>
        <p>
          This data is used solely to operate gameplay systems, maintain leaderboards, improve features, and ensure fair usage. We do not sell or share user data with third parties for commercial purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">6. Availability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We aim to provide stable service, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free availability. The Bot may experience downtime due to maintenance, updates, or unexpected issues.
        </p>
        <p>In some cases, data resets or adjustments may occur when required for system stability or feature updates.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">7. Suspension and Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to restrict, suspend, or terminate access to the Bot for users or servers that violate these Terms or engage in abusive behavior. We may also remove data associated with such violations where necessary.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The Bot is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">To the maximum extent permitted by law, we are not responsible for:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-0 list-none">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Loss of data</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Service interruptions or downtime</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Damages resulting from Bot usage</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm mt-1.5 flex-none">→</span><span>Indirect, incidental, or consequential losses</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms of Service at any time. Continued use of the Bot after updates become effective constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tightest mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions, support, privacy requests, or data-related inquiries, please contact us through our
          <a
            href="https://discord.gg/A7n88d6uRW"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-500 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700 dark:hover:text-amber-400"
          >official Discord Support Server</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-ink-900/10 dark:border-cream-100/10">
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 dark:text-cream-300/60">
          &copy; 2026 Vanillate. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
